":2517303,"uid":331631,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:59:03.000Z","msg":"你做狗仔狗女<br />\n本身心理上都覺得比人欺凌<br />\n然後人地無論做乜你都覺得係欺凌你<br />\n<br />\n好啦，你返學校，人地老師學生跪拜你啦，你又覺得人地欺凌你"},{"pid":"47b8ea6c92a7cf4546c230ac7b3774b5848c9760","tid":2517303,"uid":185565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:00:59.000Z","msg":"不協條 屌你又主觀又空泛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同學一定要同你傾計同你玩？<br />\n老師嚴啲惡啲又唔俾？<br />\n<br />\n一間學校實有邊緣人㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果咁計真係戥舊時啲邊緣學生唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n剛好你老豆老母唔係狗隻<br />\n如果唔係冚世界都要討好你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88702dd04b17f7f188fc19ce969cb87b21a9cc2","tid":2517303,"uid":133534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:02:00.000Z","msg":"狗仔狗女<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0369d7d84bab6df1cd1fa49ee1273e3fc2b3ab22","tid":2517303,"uid":35712,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:05:49.000Z","msg":"保護老師 請同學出多兩錢力蝦鳩d狗仔狗女<br />\n去多d無cctv地方發生意外 記住你地係無本咁蝦佢<br />\n記得死口否應唔關自己事<br />\n學校唔會想搞大件事登報"},{"pid":"0bb8118cf26fd41ea84ff0baeba8c15007653925","tid":2517303,"uid":40932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:07:34.000Z","msg":"不如起警察學校<br />\n俾d狗仔狗女去讀<br />\n到時出黎要做番狗"},{"pid":"3dbc2d07d249ac45c1cf2771d81d41d038ff0519","tid":2517303,"uid":384207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:09:37.000Z","msg":"唔同狗仔狗女玩係咪冇書讀?"},{"pid":"07ee80cb5516bf540d58bf623c60495d2e2d7250","tid":2517303,"uid":30113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:09:47.000Z","msg":"請問邊個無辜係無辜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=